{"tid":713073,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥斯達黎加....","createTime":"2018-06-22T14:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T14:47:24.000Z","uid":59518,"like":4,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5b47537eb521c00f05cd6ec5e51183d55a666cdd","tid":713073,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我老豆<br />\n我本身冇睇開波<br />\n頭先咁啱望到VIUTV播世界杯 見到巴西隻右翼好勁扭晒成隊<br />\n心諗一定係尼馬啦(淨係聽過佢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 尼馬咁勁一個人扭晒條右路嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 哥斯達黎加<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n補時2:0個陣我又問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咦點解尼馬助攻比尼馬嘅?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 哥斯達黎加<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">右邊嗰個哥斯達嚟架</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌原來我一直認錯右邊個個係尼馬 <br />\n成日聽佢個大名 估唔到原來左邊又插水又比人偷波嘅先係佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下條友平時係咪都係咁上下料同冇品? 點解咁出名?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba063a8f04ebf3746ad0ab74c19a41aa9263f564","tid":713073,"uid":12441,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c5da22af18918de825d1f917b3654203007d21","tid":713073,"uid":14460,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"c259fd383cc5b9016cedd3d0c986bddc36c108c7","tid":713073,"uid":59518,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"負皮 上一頁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尼馬咪右路出左下over the rainbow幾撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOP冇睇波好好反省下"},{"pid":"074b1ccf98d94112260e5958b88d98605e7fe801","tid":713073,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:21:41.000Z","msg":"咁左邊咪巴西囉？"},{"pid":"9caa8c51b6493537f751ccb8fbe8afd97694f549","tid":713073,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"6.5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfa46243f893a1402dab875b8c1e03a8c3ba3d7","tid":713073,"uid":14965,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"乜撚野尼馬傳比尼馬"},{"pid":"0417261aed564113458ea2ad03275646511e8ec8","tid":713073,"uid":190066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e69c17197e40611eabb8218f30a5aef1407eddc","tid":713073,"uid":186181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"0a5c943cac3190e243ef1614f41b2368adfc4a85","tid":713073,"uid":168924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"條友真係唔識架喎"},{"pid":"901ec356167f9c1d5a3c7c29a202dc7bf15a333f","tid":713073,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/s